QuestData.Title: Facing the Invaders
QuestData.Description:
While we try to figure out what to do with those channelers, we'll have to take shots where we can get them.
Our men could use some assistance retaking parts of the lower walls. Kill some naga for me, would you?
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay $1oa of the naga forces invading Fort Daelin.
QuestData.RewardText: Each one you killed is one less my men have to worry about. Thanks.
